message.body: Bb, what are you up to?
I'm hanging out with tim... You should visit!!!
Funny story about your text and how goofy i am. Plans tonight?
Hmm, I need to be here editing, but other than that, no! ;)
I'm jealous of the people who find you when you're not editing :(
Well I just did this baptism and I have a wedding Coming up this weekend... I try to take breaks for all my friends I care about, including you, bb
Oh I know sweets. Work is important. I just like seeing you is all and im always striking out on timing.
I know, we still need to hit up the loring pasta bar!!
Agh yes! I have the coupon for that ;)
